OL,3,CUK can 'defy' gloomy forecasts despite
OL,4,Cproductivity problems, says Chancellor
OL,6,FBritain does not have to "accept" grim
OL,7,Feconomic forecasts, Rachel Reeves has
OL,8,Finsisted despite reports she faces a
OL,9,Fbarrage of fiscal bad news ahead of
OL,10,Fnext month's Budget.
OL,12,FWriting in the Guardian, the
OL,13,FChancellor acknowledged that
OL,14,Fproductivity forecasts from the Office
OL,15,Ffor Budget Responsibility (OBR) could
OL,16,Fmake for tough reading.
OL,18,FAnd she argued that austerity, Brexit
OL,19,Fand the pandemic had left "deep scars"
OL,20,Fon the UK's economy.
