OL,3,CUK can 'defy' gloomy forecasts despite
OL,4,Cproductivity problems, says Chancellor
OL,6,FBut she said she was "determined that
OL,7,Fwe don't simply accept the forecasts
OL,8,Fbut we defy them" and would not
OL,9,F"relitigate the past or let past
OL,10,Fmistakes determine our future".
OL,12,FHer comments come as she prepares to
OL,13,Fdeliver a Budget next month widely
OL,14,Fexpected to involve further tax rises
OL,15,Fas she seeks to close a multi-billion
OL,16,Fpound gap in her plans.
