OL,3,CUK can 'defy' gloomy forecasts despite
OL,4,Cproductivity problems, says Chancellor
OL,6,FThe Institute for Fiscal Studies (IFS)
OL,7,Fwarned earlier this month that Ms
OL,8,FReeves could need to find #22 billion
OL,9,Fof tax rises or spending cuts if she
OL,10,Fis to restore the #10 billion of
OL,11,Fheadroom she left herself against her
OL,12,Fdebt targets in the spring.
OL,14,FThat gap is the result of higher
OL,15,Fborrowing costs, more persistent
OL,16,Finflation and weaker growth, along
OL,17,Fwith spending commitments such as
OL,18,Fpartially reversing the cut to winter
OL,19,Ffuel payments and watering down its
OL,20,Fplans to cut welfare.
