OL,3,CUK can 'defy' gloomy forecasts despite
OL,4,Cproductivity problems, says Chancellor
OL,6,FThis could leave the Chancellor with a
OL,7,Fgap of almost #30 billion, even before
OL,8,Fshe tries to pay for the expected
OL,9,Fabolition of the two-child benefit cap.
OL,11,FWriting in the Times, former
OL,12,Fchancellor Sir Jeremy Hunt described
OL,13,Fthe downgrade as a "hammer blow" to Ms
OL,14,FReeves' plans and urged her to
OL,15,F"transform" public sector productivity.
OL,17,FIn a further blow to the Chancellor,
OL,18,Fthe Times also reported that
OL,19,Fhousebuilders had written to the OBR
OL,20,Fwarning that Labour would not meet its
OL,21,Ftarget to build 1.5 million new homes.
