OL,3,CUK can 'defy' gloomy forecasts despite
OL,4,Cproductivity problems, says Chancellor
OL,6,FThe letter is likely to harm prospects
OL,7,Ffor the watchdog upgrading its
OL,8,Fforecast for economic growth from
OL,9,Fconstruction.
OL,11,FIn her Guardian article, Ms Reeves
OL,12,Fsaid she would not "pre-empt" the OBR
OL,13,Fproductivity downgrade, but added she
OL,14,Fwould be "candid" that Britain's
OL,15,Fproductivity performance under the
OL,16,FConservatives had been "too weak".
OL,18,FIn response, she appeared to rule our
OL,19,Fdeeper spending cuts, vowing there
OL,20,Fwould be "no return to austerity".
