OL,4,Cproductivity problems, says Chancellor
OL,6,FShe said: "If productivity is our
OL,7,Fchallenge, then investment is our
OL,8,Fsolution."
OL,10,FBut she also appeared to rule out
OL,11,Fincreases in borrowing, saying
OL,12,Finvestment "cannot come at the cost of
OL,13,Feconomic responsibility".
OL,15,FWithout deeper spending cuts or
OL,16,Fincreased borrowing, the Chancellor
OL,17,Fwill be left with little choice but to
OL,18,Fraise taxes.
